videos.description: Louisville's Christen Cunningham bouncess a pass between two defenders to find Khwan Fore for a wide-open dunk.
videos.headline: Louisville's nifty bounce pass leads to Fore's dunk

videos.description: Pittsburgh freshman Trey McGowens catches an outlet pass and slices through the Louisville defense to finish a contested layup.
videos.headline: Pitt's McGowens goes coast-to-coast for layup

videos.description: Louisville runs in transition and Ryan McMahon leaves it for Jordan Nwora, who slams it home.
videos.headline: Nwora's dunk extends Louisville's lead
